{"tid":1701980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[DGX] 聲明: 願榮光一曲從沒授權第三方賣周邊  大家小心唔好被呃","createTime":"2019-11-09T12:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T06:00:27.000Z","uid":105976,"like":77,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b6b08b6b1ee01efdd889d4109c178cab5c00b004","tid":1701980,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"繼上次hk apploc唔識串之後<br />\n今日團隊發現原來有好多間 賣teeshirt / 手機殼 /電子音樂盒 等等唔同公司<br />\n係未經聯絡 同冇授權情況下<br />\n賣 或 義賣 有關願榮光歸香港 (歌曲或歌詞) 既產品<br />\n<br />\nfc: 一首歌入面 歌曲同歌詞都係有版權保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/intellectualProperty/all.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FintellectualProperty%2Fall.shtml&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=fedaaca5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/intellectualProperty/all.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n首先重申一次 歡迎大家非商業 &amp; 為左民主自由 而使用歌曲<br />\n<br />\n而任何涉及商業既情況請先聯絡以取得我地批準<br />\n建議相關產品既公司將你地懷疑侵權既產品下架同盡快聯絡我地<br />\n<br />\nofficial site: <a href=\"https://dgxmusic.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdgxmusic.com%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=4556f58b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dgxmusic.com/</a><br />\ncopyright application: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/QuHMwJgbePD74sDEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FQuHMwJgbePD74sDEA&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=44d42318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/QuHMwJgbePD74sDEA</a><br />\ncontact email: contact@dgxmusic.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDgx<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n______________________________<br />\n順便推一推我地官網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://dgxmusic.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdgxmusic.com%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=4556f58b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dgxmusic.com/</a><br />\n有得免費下載各音樂 想支持我地既可以入itunes買歌<br />\n<br />\n最近會有後續計劃 黎緊會有新歌招人唱<br />\n<br />\n歡迎關注我地官網同FB頁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dgxmusic/?modal=admin_todo_tour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdgxmusic%2F%3Fmodal%3Dadmin_todo_tour&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=9ed40198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dgxmusic/?modal=admin_todo_tour</a><br />\n<br />\n____________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住做實事 入左罷工group未阿?<br />\n入頻道 <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=d81d84f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n再搵返你對應行業既group &gt; 未有就睇指示點樣申請開group開公會<br />\n唔好偷懶啦!"},{"pid":"fc2ca6707523c17420a52cf12c80bed0cbddbfc0","tid":1701980,"uid":38737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"不屈進行曲"},{"pid":"3fbe240560d2e1452ca48f8b139b5e1977df4033","tid":1701980,"uid":156096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"***眾籌***<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先52%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=d38941ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=9d9d947a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1322ac89fef8c2258535fc9a843491b0efa12971","tid":1701980,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2ca6707523c17420a52cf12c80bed0cbddbfc0","tid":1701980,"uid":38737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"不屈進行曲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"冇人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf83bee38ae3612661c0701be9324cc2f9b62fe","tid":1701980,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"我地暫時都冇周邊賣  如果真係出再通知大家"},{"pid":"a67b29d463a779074719b6fdd1288f4d004773e4","tid":1701980,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2ca6707523c17420a52cf12c80bed0cbddbfc0","tid":1701980,"uid":38737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"不屈進行曲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"冇人整不屈周邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02665990e784b60ea59393eab943cde1ca17d13d","tid":1701980,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=